          "reviewBody": "Alum of 2002. A super progressive school that combines the best of traditional and modern methods. Made up for the smallish playground by offering a host of activities - pottery, art, special ed, and off late AI.\nThe wellstocked library helped me become the writer i am today. And jyothi mams lectures on spirituality Keep coming to me during troubles and good times :)\n\nJivitesh Sir, the current Pricipal, is very proactive and has given the school a complete makeover!",
