            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the worst schools with rude administrators and principal. Went for the admission of both my kids aged 4+ years (twins) in UKG. My kids also appeared for a written test. They judged them so hard in interview even if it was their first visit to any school post covid. They told us our kids are below standard. Mind you they were just 4+ years old. What's more they also asked us to give us an undertaking in written that the teachers are not responsible for the performance of the students, jst because session started in Mar-April, and we went to admission in end of April (it was late by their standard).",
          "publisher": {
